title: New Zealand quake kills at least 65
author: Unknown
text: Rescuers search a collapsed building for survivors Tuesday after a magnitude-6.3 earthquake hit Christchurch, New Zealand's second-largest city. The death toll was expected to rise.Caption:  photoMartin Hunter / Getty Images: Rescuers search a collapsed building for survivors Tuesday after a magnitude-6.3 earthquake hit Christchurch, New Zealand's second-largest city.
